<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span><span class="c2">(١٠٨٨)</span> -<span class="c5"> (حديث:</span> <span class="c1">" اسعوا فإن الله كتب عليكم السعى "</span> <span class="c2">(ص ٢٦١)</span> .<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
